stom icon management:"},"448":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-62","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icon-apis","content":"**`set(icons)`**: Synchronously add icons to the store"},"449":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-63","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icon-apis","content":"**`ondemand(loader)`**: Register an asynchronous icon loader (returns unregister function)"},"450":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-64","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icon-apis","content":"**`parser(svgString)`**: Parse SVG strings into React elements"},"451":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-65","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#custom-icon-apis","content":"These are re-exports of the underlying Bento Icon system methods. For complete API documentation, advanced usage patterns, and implementation details, see the `@bento/icon` and `@bento/svg-parser` package documentation."},"452":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-66","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#notes","content":"Custom icons integrate seamlessly with all Icon component features (transformations, accessibility, sprite mode, etc.)"},"453":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-67","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#notes","content":"Multiple `ondemand` loaders can be registered and will be called in order until one returns content"},"454":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-68","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#notes","content":"Use the `parser` function to convert SVG strings to React elements"},"455":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-69","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#notes","content":"Custom icons are cached automatically just like CDN icons"},"456":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-70","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#css-classes","content":"The component accepts standard `className` and `style` props:"},"457":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-71","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#css-classes","content":"**Important**: When you supply a `className`, you make a commitment to take over all styling of the component as it will remove the standard class names. Use data attributes for targeted styling instead."},"458":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-72","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#data-attributes","content":"The component automatically adds data attributes for styling hooks:"},"459":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-73","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#data-attributes","content":"`data-icon`: The icon name (always present)"},"460":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-74","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#data-attributes","content":"`data-color`: Applied when color prop is set"},"461":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-75","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#data-attributes","content":"`data-loading`: Applied during icon loading from CDN"},"462":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-76","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#data-attributes","content":"`data-mode`: Applied when mode prop is set (e.g., \"sprite\")"},"463":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-77","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#data-attributes","content":"`data-flip`: Applied when flip prop is set (\"horizontal\" or \"vertical\")"},"464":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-78","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#data-attributes","content":"`data-rotate`: Applied when rotate prop is set (90, 180, or 270)"},"465":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-79","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#data-attributes","content":"The component also includes accessibility attributes:"},"466":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-80","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#data-attributes","content":"`role=\"presentation\"`: For decorative icons"},"467":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-81","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#data-attributes","content":"`role=\"img\"`: When title prop is provided"},"468":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-82","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#data-attributes","content":"`focusable=\"false\"`: Prevents keyboard focus"},"469":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-83","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#inherit-from-parent-default","content":"By default, icons inherit the color from their parent element via `currentColor`:"},"470":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-84","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#explicit-colors","content":"Override the color with specific values:"},"471":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-85","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#icon-transformations","content":"Transform capabilities are inherited from the Bento Illustration component. For complete transformation options and implementation details, see the `@bento/illustration` package documentation."},"472":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-86","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#rotation","content":"Rotate icons by 90-degree increments:"},"473":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-87","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#flipping","content":"Flip icons horizontally or vertically:"},"474":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-88","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#placeholder-content","content":"Provide fallback SVG content while icons load from the CDN:"},"475":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-89","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#decorative-icons","content":"For purely decorative icons, no additional attributes are needed. The icon will have `role=\"presentation\"` and be ignored by screen readers:"},"476":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-90","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#semantic-icons","content":"For icons that convey meaning, use the `title` prop. This automatically adds `role=\"img\"` and provides screen reader accessible text:"},"477":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-91","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#interactive-icons","content":"For interactive icons within buttons or links, use the `title` prop on the icon and `aria-label` on the interactive element:"},"478":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-92","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loading","content":"Icons are loaded on-demand from a CDN using the following process:"},"479":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-93","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loading","content":"**First Request**: When an icon is first encountered, it triggers an asynchronous fetch from the CDN"},"480":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-94","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#default-icon-loading","content":"**SVG Parsing**: The fetched SVG string is parsed into a React element using `@bento/svg-parser`"},"481":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-95","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],