ny times it's used"},"489":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-103","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**Client-Side Hydration**: The sprite sheet is generated and injected after hydration, causing a brief paint event"},"490":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-104","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**DOM Output:**"},"491":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-105","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**Performance Benefits:**"},"492":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-106","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**Reduced DOM Size**: Path data stored once instead of duplicated"},"493":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-107","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**Lower Memory Usage**: Especially beneficial with many repeated icons"},"494":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-108","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**Faster Rendering**: Browser optimizations for `<use>` elements"},"495":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-109","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**Trade-offs:**"},"496":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-110","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**SSR Limitation**: Sprite references render empty until client-side hydration"},"497":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-111","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#sprite-mode-optimization","content":"**Initial Flash**: Brief moment where icons appear/disappear during sprite injection"},"498":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-112","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#recommendations","content":"**Use default mode** for SSR applications or when icons appear infrequently"},"499":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-113","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#recommendations","content":"**Use sprite mode** when the same icons appear many times (navigation, lists, tables)"},"500":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-114","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#recommendations","content":"**Consider preloading** frequently used icons to reduce loading delays"},"501":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-115","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#recommendations","content":"**Provide fallback content** for critical icons to handle loading states"},"502":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-116","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#icon-not-loading","content":"If an icon fails to load:"},"503":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-117","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#icon-not-loading","content":"**Check icon name**: Ensure the icon exists in the CDN"},"504":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-118","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#icon-not-loading","content":"**Network connectivity**: Verify CDN is accessible"},"505":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-119","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#icon-not-loading","content":"**Check browser console**: Look for network errors"},"506":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-120","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#icon-not-loading","content":"**Fallback content**: Provide placeholder content for loading states"},"507":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-121","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#performance-issues","content":"For performance optimization:"},"508":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-122","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#performance-issues","content":"**Preload common icons**: Consider preloading frequently used icons"},"509":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-123","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#performance-issues","content":"**Use sprite mode**: For repeated icons, consider sprite mode which consolidates multiple icons into a single SVG sprite sheet, reducing DOM size and improving performance when the same icon appears multiple times"},"510":{"id":"/docs/components/icon-124","page_id":"/docs/components/icon","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/icon#performance-issues","content":"**Minimize icon sets**: Only load icons that are actually used"},"511":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","type":"page","content":"FileTrigger","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/file-trigger"},"512":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-0","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/file-trigger","content":"A style-less primitive that wraps any pressable component and opens the native file picker when it is activated."},"513":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-1","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#features","content":"Features"},"514":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-2","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#installation","content":"Installation"},"515":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-3","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#props","content":"Props"},"516":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-4","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#examples","content":"Examples"},"517":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-5","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#basic-usage","content":"Basic Usage"},"518":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-6","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#accepted-types","content":"Accepted Types"},"519":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-7","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#accessibility","content":"Accessibility"},"520":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-8","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#best-practices","content":"Best Practices"},"521":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-9","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#features","content":"Turns any pressable component (such as an Antares `Button`) into a file picker trigger."},"522":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-10","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#features","content":"Renders a visually hidden `<input type=\"file\">` — no styling of its own."},"523":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-11","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#features","content":"Restricts selection by MIME type, allows multiple files, directory selection, and camera capture."},"524":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-12","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#features","content":"Resets the input value before every open, so re-selecting the same file still fires `onSelect`."},"525":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-13","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#basic-usage","content":"Wrap any pressable component. Activating the child opens the native file picker; the selected files arrive in `onSelect`."},"526":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-14","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#accepted-types","content":"Restrict the picker to specific MIME types with `acceptedFileTypes`, and allow more than one file with `allowsMultiple`."},"527":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-15","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#accessibility","content":"`FileTrigger` adds no visuals or ARIA of its own — accessibility comes from the pressable child you provide. Use a component with an accessible name (e.g. an Antares `Button` with clear label text) so assistive technology announces the action. The underlying `<input>` is visually hidden but remains operable by keyboard through the child's press behavior."},"528":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-16","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#best-practices","content":"`acceptedFileTypes` is a best-effort filter for the OS picker — always validate file type and size again in your `onSelect` handler, since it can be bypassed."},"529":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-17","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#best-practices","content":"Pair `FileTrigger` with `DropZone` to offer both click-to-browse and drag-and-drop. See the DropZone \"File Upload\" example."},"530":{"id":"/docs/components/file-trigger-18","page_id":"/docs/components/file-trigger","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/file-trigger#best-practices","content":"Keep the child a single pressable element; `FileTrigger` forwards press behavior to whatever you nest inside it."},"531":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","type":"page","content":"InlineDrawer","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer"},"532":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-0","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","content":"An in-flow collapsible built on RAC Disclosure. Compose a trigger and content to make an accordion or a sidebar rail."},"533":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-1","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#features","content":"Features"},"534":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-2","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#installation","content":"Installation"},"535":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-3","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#props","content":"Props"},"536":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-4","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#examples","content":"Examples"},"537":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-5","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#basic-usage","content":"Basic Usage"},"538":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-6","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#controlled","content":"Controlled"},"539":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-7","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#sidebar-navigation","content":"Sidebar Navigation"},"5