page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#features","content":"Controlled and uncontrolled modes (`isExpanded` / `defaultExpanded` / `onExpandedChange`)"},"549":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-17","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#features","content":"Accordion collapse uses the browser's `hidden=\"until-found\"` for find-in-page"},"550":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-18","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#features","content":"`prefers-reduced-motion` support"},"551":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-19","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#props","content":"The `InlineDrawerPanel` component accepts the following props:"},"552":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-20","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#basic-usage","content":"Put a `<Button slot=\"trigger\">` and an `<InlineDrawerPanel>` inside `InlineDrawer`. The panel hides when collapsed and animates open."},"553":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-21","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#controlled","content":"Use `isExpanded` and `onExpandedChange` to drive state externally."},"554":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-22","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#sidebar-navigation","content":"A rail whose content stays visible when collapsed is a composition, not a mode: drive `isExpanded` yourself, render always-visible children (no `InlineDrawerPanel`), and let `minSize`/`maxSize` size the rail. Use numeric (px) sizes so the width animates; intrinsic keywords like `min-content`/`max-content` fit the content exactly but don't animate."},"555":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-23","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#keyboard","content":"Key"},"556":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-24","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#keyboard","content":"Action"},"557":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-25","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#keyboard","content":"`Enter` / `Space`"},"558":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-26","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#keyboard","content":"Toggle via the slotted trigger"},"559":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-27","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#keyboard","content":"`Tab`"},"560":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-28","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#keyboard","content":"Move focus through the content"},"561":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-29","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#aria","content":"A `<Button slot=\"trigger\">` gets `aria-expanded` + `aria-controls` wired to the `InlineDrawerPanel` automatically (via RAC Disclosure)."},"562":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-30","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#aria","content":"For the sidebar rail, the toggle is your own control (e.g. a `ToggleButton`) — give icon-only buttons an `aria-label`, and the content stays in the DOM and accessible since nothing is hidden."},"563":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-31","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#best-practices","content":"Accordion → `Button slot=\"trigger\"` + `InlineDrawerPanel`. Sidebar rail → controlled state + always-visible children."},"564":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-32","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#best-practices","content":"For the rail, use numeric (px) `minSize`/`maxSize` so the width animates; `min-content`/`max-content` fit the content exactly but won't animate."},"565":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-33","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#best-practices","content":"`placement` does not flip in RTL; the side is decided by document/flex order."},"566":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-34","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#best-practices","content":"Don't nest InlineDrawers."},"567":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox","page_id":"/docs/components/listbox","type":"page","content":"ListBox","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/listbox"},"568":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox-0","page_id":"/docs/components/listbox","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/listbox","content":"ListBox is a selectable collection of items rendered inline. Use it for non-popover pickers, inline lists, or as a building block for higher-level components like Select."},"569":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox-1","page_id":"/docs/components/listbox","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/listbox#features","content":"Features"},"570":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox-2","page_id":"/docs/components/listbox","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/listbox#installation","content":"Installation"},"571":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox-3","page_id":"/docs/components/listbox","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/listbox#props","content":"Props"},"572":{"id":"/docs/components/listbox-4","pa